To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private TripleExponentialMovingAverage _tema;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_tema = TEMA(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_tema.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "tripleexponentialmovingaverage", _tema.Current.Value);
}
